entries.journal_entry_description: Colonel Panaka suggests that you go to Coronet on Corellia and speak with Lt. Jasper of the Corellian Security Force.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Greetings, Colonel Panaka here. If you're looking for more work, I thought you might be interested in speaking with a colleague of mine on Corellia. His name is Lt. Jasper and he works for the Corellian Security Force. Go speak with him.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Greetings, Colonel Panaka here. If you're looking for more work, I thought you might be interested in speaking with a colleague of mine on Corellia. His name is Lt. Jasper and he works for the Corellian Security Force. Go speak with him.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Speak with Lieutenant Jasper of the Corellian Security Force. You'll find him in Coronet on Corellia.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Speak with Lieutenant Jasper on Corellia
